Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:39.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:44.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:50.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:53.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:59.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:04.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:07.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:07.66,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.90,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:17.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:20.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:24.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:28.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:35.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:39.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:50.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.53,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界將要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:39.10,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果註定難逃死滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:44.10,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟該相信什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:50.10,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:53.80,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必體會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:59.73,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}這撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:04.43,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}響徹在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:07.66,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的鎮魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:11.81,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.90,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然從飄乎的現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:17.25,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找尋你的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:20.85,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:24.58,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:28.83,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都歷歷在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.87,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因為曾經深愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:35.63,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:39.40,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}殘留的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:43.55,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:50.48,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Comment: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,=============STORY===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要文化遺產調查？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不能在規定時間內完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種景點怎麼可能有任務嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想約我去玩就直說好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是去玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很認真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 跟我一起接受這個任務吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風很誠心地請伊札那和他去兩天一夜的旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是去千秋鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是千秋鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來 長道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 湊近一點看更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊…伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,任 務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知各修理班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總監命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優先使用資材倉庫中所保存的建材及裝甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 大部分補好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 紬你今天一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是孤單寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隨時都可以跟你掌位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打 你真是有夠下流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 不能搭理這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟我一起飛飛看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請手下留情喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你抓牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長 長道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是要調查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是希德尼婭最棒的賞櫻勝地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 扶手沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著是那邊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了啦 不用裝成是在調查的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地板連接處正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 我查到潛入千秋鄉的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地圖我發給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你幫忙的事也寫在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能讓他們在千秋鄉兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是定期檢查的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被褥 無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查這種地方做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著就是確認防護門的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不安分點是不會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 得調查才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防護門 運作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一項是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在千秋鄉待命到明天10:00為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說待在這裡就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 就這點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我哪知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個水池明明是無重力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水卻沒有飛出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是水池啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是 這是浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫無重力環境專用浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是非常奢侈的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…我們來泡一泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次真想把紬也帶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟她喜歡泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起來泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這字…是奶奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些全都是奶奶教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險 伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等 聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道你根本不在乎我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.99,eyecatch,NTP,1050,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　千秋鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.04,eyecatch,NTP,994,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　外周壁居住區屋簷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實仔細想想 兩個人單獨出去過夜也不一定就會發生什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說谷風和伊札那在我們住進來之前就是兩個人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那時候伊札那還沒開始女性化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然說不要潛入千秋鄉的是紬你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就別再介意了 快睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纈小姐你不也是介意得睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生會不會也請我去那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 那時我聽到他們說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道你根本不在乎我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢 谷風是怎麼回答的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是覺得偷聽是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 纈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請忘了剛才的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日凌晨 希德尼婭已進入雷姆星系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz357.4\pos(624,184)}終於進入雷姆星系！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz357.4\pos(738,506)}將加強戰時供給管制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部隨之宣佈將提升警戒態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及加強戰時供給管制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於走到這一步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真的是希德尼婭現在該走的路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移民到行星七號的人怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然無法取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十有八九…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星九號我們無論如何都必須拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能拿下這裡將決定戰局的走向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這顆行星作為天然要害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將在與大眾合船交戰時成為重要據點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在先給我爭取點時間啊 小林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第三特編班 衛人用高速自主支援裝甲的……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 它在分離狀態下也能衝進大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃在對行星九號進行偵察的同時也測試測試這部「隼風」的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是對奇居子發動自殺式攻擊用的棺材嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芯的前端還周到地裝上了人工穎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這些有一堆替補的操縱士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開著這東西往大眾合船裡衝就行了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 少說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 這次的偵察任務把她搞得有點神經質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 就算我是總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會為了區區一次偵察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就動用那邊那種昂貴的最新機型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和像你這樣的精英吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼婭就拜託你了啊 英雄大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想看到王牌糾結的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我是科戶瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說本來明天要出偵察任務的人抗命被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就換我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二套裝備換得太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察任務也是實戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別給我撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第4第5工作台 快往後移
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別妨礙搬運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准慣性控制機關的最終檢查可別偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊裝備檢查 確認已更換為第二套裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊裝備確認無誤後 操縱士開始上機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊的機體與隼風連接後立即前往行星九號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我方無法觀測的區域進行偵察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後迅速回航希德尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊 出擊準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星九號偵察部隊 已出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著準備射出隼風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊 開始掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維持現有隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎噴射防護壁 關閉準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央發射口 隔離壁全部打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駐座懸吊裝置 固定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射口 通道正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速自主支援裝甲「隼風」 出擊準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼風 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}隼風 開始引導偵察隊向掌位中心靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科戶瀨 你太靠內了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維持掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行速度同步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼風 減速至可連結速度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將到達接觸點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向與偵察隊同步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謹慎行事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對速度微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼風 裝甲打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊與隼風 飛行速度已同步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始連結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 慢慢靠過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊 維持掌位態勢接近隼風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體連結成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連結已成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 行星九號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大動力前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮定點啊 谷風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一次待命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就是在這兒急也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去散散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好擔心伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想和她一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊報告總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將進入行星九號背面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子很擅長藏身 萬事小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正通過星環附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截至目前一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科戶瀨 新雷達上有什麼反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我這裡也沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠看明明那麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近看起來就只是一堆髒兮兮的石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且感覺奇居子隨時可能從陰影裡跳出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是平靜不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別光顧著星環了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要到達距行星九號的最近點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科戶瀨 怎麼了？看到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 慢慢把意識移回雷達上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航路前方出現了一團霧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧？什麼都看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射希格斯粒子炮試試
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可視化的奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 準備閃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標太大了 來不及迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼衝過去的話或許能把牠打穿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊 放棄隼風 迅速閃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全機分離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H79E9EB&\fs40\frz5.976\pos(730,546)}人工穎反應消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芯沒能貫穿奇居子就被破壞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這胞衣不單純
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 這膜越變越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
